      <title>德意志银行聘请瑞银的 Aly Alibhai 领导北美并购业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/deutsche-bank-hires-ubs-s-aly-alibhai-to-lead-north-american-m-a</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，德意志银行已聘请瑞银集团媒体和娱乐银行家 Aly Alibhai 担任北美并购主管。]]></description>
