      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 14:58:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币价格从 7 月以来的最高水平回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/bitcoin-tops-67-000-to-reach-highest-level-since-july</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国大选临近，数字资产领域波动性重现，比特币价格两个多月来首次突破 67,000 美元，抹去了早前的涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/bitcoin-tops-67-000-to-reach-highest-level-since-july</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 14:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥迪拒绝所有可能关闭的电动汽车工厂报价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/audi-rejects-offers-for-troubled-brussels-electric-vehicle-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大众汽车集团旗下的高端品牌奥迪未能为其位于布鲁塞尔陷入困境的电动汽车工厂找到合适的投资者，这增加了该工厂关闭的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/audi-rejects-offers-for-troubled-brussels-electric-vehicle-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 13:46:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>道达尔将支持莫桑比克天然气码头以增加进口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/total-set-to-back-mozambique-lng-terminal-to-boost-gas-imports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[道达尔能源公司计划明年批准在莫桑比克设立液化天然气进口终端，这可能有助于邻国南非的用户避免潜在的供应危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/total-set-to-back-mozambique-lng-terminal-to-boost-gas-imports</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 11:30:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波音公司将筹集最多 250 亿美元资金以避免现金短缺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/boeing-reaches-10-billion-credit-pact-to-shore-up-balance-sheet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波音公司朝着筹集高达 250 亿美元的目标迈进了一步，这笔资金将为这家陷入困境的飞机制造商提供财务资源，以抵御一场造成严重破坏的罢工，并克服一系列运营障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/boeing-reaches-10-billion-credit-pact-to-shore-up-balance-sheet</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 10:33:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>铜价跌至三周低点，因市场对中国局势再度担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/copper-slides-to-three-week-low-on-fresh-jitters-over-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场对政府的促增长举措对需求究竟有多大影响存疑，基本金属也跟随中国风险资产遭遇抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/copper-slides-to-three-week-low-on-fresh-jitters-over-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 07:09:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
